送ﾙRarchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/blog/2020-06-12-twin0042.mdﾙ@93fa0a259cbc2edfcb046801d3c87036a7827820610a3c5d553a3f48c3b445a0ｳThis week in Nu #42袖This week in Nu #42ﾚﾑutam0k added an option to 
``mkdir``
 to 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1932] show the paths being created
JosephTLyons 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1940] removed async_stream from some commands
 (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1951] 2
), fixed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1944] spaces in test paths
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1945] updated 
``cal``
,
samhedin added support for 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1943] per-directory environment variables
arashout improved 
``to toml``
 to 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1946] disallow top-level values
daschl made 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1952] interruptible streams public
jonathandturner renamed the ".env" file to 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1953] ".nu-env"
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1955] released 0.15.0
, fixed a bug with 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1966] operator precedence
, add support for 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1967] readonly config files
, and move a 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1970] batch of commands off async_stream
svartalf fixed an issue with process usage and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1954] bumped the heim dependency
Also!
We've added our 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/rfcs] initial RFC process
. Come let us know what you think.
註接Title: This week in Nu #42
Path: This week in Nu #42
Content:
utam0k added an option to 
``mkdir``
 to 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1932] show the paths being created
JosephTLyons 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1940] removed async_stream from some commands
 (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1951] 2
), fixed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1944] spaces in test paths
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1945] updated 
``cal``
,
samhedin added support for 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1943] per-directory environment variables
arashout improved 
``to toml``
 to 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1946] disallow top-level values
daschl made 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1952] interruptible streams public
jonathandturner renamed the ".env" file to 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1953] ".nu-env"
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1955] released 0.15.0
, fixed a bug with 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1966] operator precedence
, add support for 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1967] readonly config files
, and move a 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1970] batch of commands off async_stream
svartalf fixed an issue with process usage and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1954] bumped the heim dependency
Also!
We've added our 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/rfcs] initial RFC process
. Come let us know what you think.
